This section demonstrates how to interact with The Movie Database (TMDb) API using Python. It covers setting up your API key, defining the endpoint, creating a request with proper parameters, and parsing the JSON response. The tutorial is essential for fetching dynamic movie data like titles, overviews, and images.


#.          API Tutorial
# ~ Go settings, API and get API key, Copy API key and paste ~

